{"tid":1434164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請比我三十秒","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:35:55.000Z","uid":178896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7973139ce19e23afbbf5bafa9218951870b21af","tid":1434164,"uid":178896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"首先想講嘅係，8月5日全港三罷人數<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">超過35萬</span></span>，真係好好好多謝您哋願意為香港出一份力！<br />\n<br />\n其次，希望香港人能謹記。無論您係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span></span>抑或是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武派</span></span>，我哋永遠都係一家人。就算發生咩事都要一齊共同進退，成為彼此最強嘅後盾！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後，希望各位手足堅持落去，繼續努力。<br />\n我深信我哋必能戰勝黑暗，迎來光明！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SHZEuA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SHZEuA.gif&h=2cb78855&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}